==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interplead
<hw>In`ter*plead"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <fld>(Law)</fld>
<def>To plead against each other, or go to trial between themselves, as
the claimants in an in an interpleader. See <er>Interpleader</er>.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>enterplead</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interpleader</ent>⟦br⟧
